Brady Bluhm https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Brady_Bluhm 0 Brady Bluhm (born July 6, 1983) is an American actor. He played Christopher Robin in many Winnie the Pooh films. He has also played roles in Dumb and Dumber, its sequel Dumb and Dumber To, and the TV series Get a Life. Bluhm is a member of The Church of Jesus Christ of Latter-day Saints and served an LDS Mission in Concepción, Chile. Bluhm resides in Rancho Cucamonga, California with his wife, Abbie, their daughter, Faye, and their other children. Brady_Bluhm ( born July_6_,_1983 ) is an_American_actor .
